to clear my name. Can I trust him?)

00:12:51.639 --> 00:12:53.120
You're truly wise, my mentor.

00:12:53.960 --> 00:12:56.240
I'm not too bad as your disciple, right?

00:13:11.039 --> 00:13:12.799
